thread.title: BRIEF-Aventus Retail Property Fund Says ‍HY Net Profit Attributable Up 16.6% To $75.0 Mln

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Aventus Retail Property Fund Says ‍HY Net Profit Attributable Up 16.6% To $75.0 Mln
text:
Feb 12 (Reuters) - Aventus Retail Property Fund:
* ‍HY NET PROFIT ATTRIBUTABLE UP 16.6% TO $75.0 MILLION​ * ‍HY REVENUE FROM ORDINARY ACTIVITIES UP 28.3 PERCENT TO $83.1 MILLION​
* ‍DEVELOPMENT EXPENDITURE FOR FY18 IS EXPECTED TO BE $35 MILLION​‍​
* EXPECTS FY18 FFO PER UNIT TO BE 2% - 3% HIGHER THAN FY17 FFO PER UNIT‍​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (bangalore.newsroom@thomsonreuters.com)
